593
01:14:55,088 --> 01:15:04,152
Switching over to the 80, by replacing the Route 350 bus with the Route 80 bus, which stops will be removed between Burlington and Cambridge with the new route?

594
01:15:05,832 --> 01:15:17,237
So the main change that would be in effect for the 80 when it goes out to Burlington, not that one, let's see, where's my 80?

595
01:15:19,872 --> 01:15:24,213
The main changes are primarily in the Arlington and Cambridge portion of the route.

596
01:15:24,673 --> 01:15:38,898
So the Burlington, North Burlington, up by, you know, LaCoshes and by the Wegmans in Burlington and by the Burlington Mall road stops for the Burlington Mall, those would generally be the same up through Winchester.

597
01:15:42,830 --> 01:15:51,997
the portions of the route where it would differ are entirely, once you get to Arlington Center, then it kind of travels over like an 80.

598
01:15:52,538 --> 01:16:00,824
So it means that it doesn't have the stops on Mass Ave between Arlington Center and Alewife Brook Parkway.

599
01:16:01,604 --> 01:16:05,327
And the only other stop that would change is the stop at Alewife Busway itself.

600
01:16:05,848 --> 01:16:08,630
But in exchange, you pick up both a Green Line

601
01:16:09,932 --> 01:16:15,276
