1285
02:32:19,322 --> 02:32:19,822
Yes, we can.

1286
02:32:20,752 --> 02:32:26,813
Yeah, so I brought this up during the breakout groups, but I know it was better to ask it during the larger meeting.

1287
02:32:27,934 --> 02:32:37,616
There is like a change in GM as I guess, I feel like a lot of people know, maybe not everybody knows, but there's an expected change in GM in a couple of months for the MBTA.

1288
02:32:38,776 --> 02:32:41,077
Does that affect anything about the Better Bus project?

1289
02:32:41,277 --> 02:32:47,118
