1291
02:32:51,112 --> 02:32:57,435
We do not anticipate that having an impact on this project.

1292
02:32:58,716 --> 02:32:58,956
Cool.

1293
02:32:59,116 --> 02:32:59,516
Thank you.

1294
02:33:00,517 --> 02:33:00,957
Thank you.

