02:33:53,760 --> 02:34:08,049
And I was thinking that we could maybe also kind of like the alternating idea with the 83, have the 426, 450 alternate during rush hours and have it at Wonderland and all other times as a suitable compromise.

1310
02:34:09,065 --> 02:34:15,590
